By adding following css would help
```css
table {
    table-layout: fixed;
    word-wrap: break-word;
}
```

![screen shot 2019-01-02 at 5 48 11 pm](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/2952415/50587004-06f47980-0eb7-11e9-9c72-b4262bd06cd5.png)

Make sense? If yes, I would like to create a pull request.
